methods.checkedClassForName:
Gets the specified className, and if it is assignable from the expectedType returns it.  Otherwise throws
 a RuntimeException.

Note: Java generics information - <T>

:param className: (java.lang.String) - the class we would like to retrieve
:param expectedType: (java.lang.Class<T>) - the type of class we expect className to be
:return: (java.lang.Class<? extends T>) the Class object for className
